repository-code: "https://github.com/Magnusvron/llm-benchmark-quality-index"
abstract: >-
  Reproducibility package for the Benchmark Quality Assurance Index (BQAI),
  a quantitative AHP-weighted framework for assessing the scientific quality
  of evaluation benchmarks used to measure Large Language Models. Contains
  the operational scoring rubric, raw evaluator data, inter-rater reliability
  analysis, AHP weight derivation, sensitivity analysis, and the model-by-benchmark
  performance matrix with source traceability.
keywords:
  - large-language-models
  - benchmarks
  - evaluation
  - reproducibility
  - AHP
  - quality-assessment
